    <section identifier="/ca-mountain-view/chapter-2/article-xiii/section-sec.-2.202"
             temporalId="sSEC_ 2_202">
      <num>SEC. 2.202</num>
      <heading>Terms defined</heading>
      <content>
        <p>The terms &quot;purchases&quot; or &quot;purchasing,&quot; as hereinafter used, shall include the terms
               &quot;contracts for&quot; or &quot;contracting for&quot; or &quot;procurement of&quot; or &quot;procure.&quot;</p>
        <p>(Ord. No. 7.16, § 1, 5/24/16.)</p>
      </content>
    </section>
  </main>
